      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/gold-xauusd-edges-up-after-record-breaking-run-triggers-profit-taking</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上一届会议下跌1.3％后，戈德在周三的狭窄乐队中交易，当时交易者从金属最新的破纪录中预订了利润。]]></description>
